                                    face="times new roman,times" size="3">
                                    <font
                                    face="times new roman,times" size="3">
                                    <font
                                    face="times new roman,times" size="3">
                                    <b>
                                    <font
                                    face="times new roman,times" size="3">
                                    <font
                                    face="Times New Roman" size="3">

                                    <font
                                    face="Times New Roman" size="3">In order to control the update semantics, in addition to the attributes below, the following will also be present:</font>
                                    </font>
                                    <font
                                    face="Times New Roman" size="3">
                                    <ul>
                                    <li>

                                    <font
                                    face="Times New Roman" size="3">An <i>updateMode</i> attribute to indicate whether the item should be "added" or "altered" (mandatory). This item cannot be removed via messaging.</font>
                                    </li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <div>
                                    <i>If used in a notification message:</i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                    <b>In addition to the attributes below, in order to specify the type of update that has occurred, the following will also be present: </b>
                                    <ul>
                                    <li>
                                    <b> An <i>updateMode</i> attribute to indicate whether the item has been "added", "altered", or is "unchanged"</b>
                                    <b> (mandatory)</b>
                                    </li>
                                    </ul>
                                    </div>
                                    </font>
                                    </font>
                                    </b>
                                    </font>
                                    </font>
                                    </font>
                                    </font>
                                    </font>
                                </font>
